OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDavid Walliams: 'Harmful'  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FChinese character removed  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffrom children's book       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A story containing "harmful            
OL,6, stereotypes" of a Chinese boy is to be 
OL,7, removed from a David Walliams          
OL,8, children's book by its publishers.     
OL,10,FHarperCollins will release a new       
OL,11,Fedition of The World's Worst Children  
OL,12,Fnext year without the story Brian Wong,
OL,13,FWho Was Never, Ever Wrong.             
OL,15,FThe move comes after podcaster Georgie 
OL,16,FMa criticised the book for "normalising
OL,17,Fjokes on minorities from a young age". 
OL,19,FAfter meeting Ma, the publishers       
OL,20,Fconfirmed the story would be replaced. 
